oney Stuff and other great Bloomberg newsletters here. Thanks![1] Fun fact,=
 I first heard about Wonderland a few months ago, after I had knee surgery =
and my physical therapist pitched me on Wonderland. =E2=80=9CIt=E2=80=99s a=
 Ponzi,=E2=80=9D he said gleefully, =E2=80=9Cbut I=E2=80=99m making a lot o=
f money.=E2=80=9D[2] Actually I am not sure this is true. The SEC rules def=
ine the term =E2=80=9Ccode of ethics=E2=80=9D to mean =E2=80=9Cwritten stan=
