</em>to the shareholder plaintiffs here</a>, meaning that they are dangerou=
s for the company,=C2=A0and the more strict and detailed they are the more =
dangerous they are. If your code of ethics says =E2=80=9Cexecutives are exp=
ected to act ethically where appropriate,=E2=80=9D and your chief executive=
